     - Nháº­n quest theo level (tween tá»›i NPC, Ä‘á»©ng 5 studs)
     - Auto farm mob: Ä‘á»©ng trÃªn Ä‘áº§u mob (cao 15 studs, khÃ´ng tá»¥t)
     - Khi mob cháº¿t â†’ tÃ¬m mob cÃ¹ng loáº¡i gáº§n nháº¥t
     - Khi khÃ´ng cÃ³ mob â†’ tween tá»›i spawn chá»
     - Attack tÃ­ch há»£p (spam RegisterAttack + RegisterHit)
     - GUI báº­t/táº¯t Auto Farm, báº­t/táº¯t Auto Stats, CHá»ŒN STAT & POINTS
